lead_paragraph: Hillary Rodham Clinton and Jeb Bush, potential foes in the 2016 presidential contest, said Monday that higher education has the power to transform lives and be a force for democracy around the globe.

headline.main: Jeb Bush, Hillary Clinton Promote Higher Education
headline.print_headline: Jeb Bush, Hillary Clinton Promote Higher Education
